pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.Parent

Class TaskViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.Parent.TaskViewController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITab

    public class TaskViewController
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITab
    This class is the controller for the "task tab" that has:

    a table view taskTV, that displays the tasks that the logged parent, returned by the method:

    PersonDAO.getLoggedParent()

    a "plus button" that opens the "add task window", managed by:

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.AddTaskController.java

    a "notifications button" that opens the "notifications window" managed by:

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.NotificationsController.java

    buttons to the other tabs: parents, kids and rewards:

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.ParentViewController.java

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.KidViewController.java

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.RewardViewController.java

    The "task tab" is in this fxml file: pt.iade.ManageeMHome.views#taskView.fxml.

    Author:
    jaime
